Life is really short & precious so you have to live everyday like it’s your last. Right now my heart is broken and I’m so torn. To even be typing this has me in a frenzy. @jerrismogul was my mentor & my bestfriend for 9 years. You finally got your wings 🕊️🫶🏾🕊️ 1/26/73 - 2/3/23. 

Words can’t describe this feeling I am feeling right now.  Thank you for believing in me, thank you for supporting my dreams, thank you for teaching me so many life lessons, thank you taking me under your wing. My confidant, my voice of reason, my friend. You were truly one of the greatest Visionaries I was able to encounter & I’m forever grateful 🥹. 

When I first met you 12 years ago on Facebook. You told me that I was going to do great things to impact the world! @obviousmag was your baby. You wanted to leave something for US as of community. Something that was created by US for US. 

Please pray for his mother, father, siblings & those that knew him. I’ve personally tried to reach to those who I could before posting. There will be a memorial service, no details are available as of now.

Happy Pride Month 🌈🌈🌈🌈🌈🌈

I’m so thankful for choosing myself so long ago! I remember when I came out it wasn’t a big spectacle, however I remember people started to move differently with me. Focusing on me and my goals was the best thing I could have did for myself in my 20s. I’m extremely humbled with how far I’ve come. At 33 I’m finally receiving all of the desires of my ❤️‍🔥 & I’m completely in Awww. I met the love of my life! GOD I'm forever grateful for you answering my 🙏🏾🙏🏾’s.  Here’s to the future! Be yourself unapologetically people will have to adjust! If they don’t oh F****** well. Continue to make ‘em uncomfortable! 

#loveislove #lovewins

As Im wrapping up my NYFW 2023 Im so humbled and grateful for another successful season with @nolchashows. It wouldn’t have come together the way it did it wasn’t for my brillant team so I want y’all to know if y’all wasn’t there things would have been a disaster! With all the obstacles we still came together and crushed it and left no crumbs. To my right hands @taliekjeqon, @iamrandyluna & @tippitimagery 

This season I produced the show at the @mercedesbenzmanhattan where we’ve completely transformed the dealership into a Fashion Experience while showcasing 9 designers. I’m thrilled that we have been asked to come back next season and do an even bigger turnout. I’m elated about the future and what’s to come. 

Here’s to the future in fashion, here’s to going harder, here’s to going HIGHER. Don’t let ppl tell you what you can do, who you can be, and most importantly how far you can go. Claim everything you desire and add tax! 🙏🏾🙏🏾🙏🏾
